zmirek and Theisen Eaton triumph in Gotzis|url=http://www.iaaf.org/news/report/kazmirek-theisen-eaton-gotzis1|publisher=IAAF|author=Diego Sampaolo|date=31 May 2015|accessdate=1 June 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|13.54 <small>(-0.2 m/s)</small>\n|28 May 2017\n|<ref>{{cite news|title=Thiam scores 7013 to break meeting record in G\u00f6tzis|url=https://www.iaaf.org/news/report/hypo-meeting-gotzis-2017-warner-thiam|publisher=IAAF|author=Diego Sampaolo|date=28 May 2017|accessdate=28 May 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Discus throw]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Norbert Demel]]|GER}}\n|55.14 m\n|28 May 1995\n|\n|-\n|[[Pole vault]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Erki Nool]]|EST}}\n|5.55 m\n|4 June 2000\n|\n|-\n|[[Javelin throw]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Leonel Suarez]]|CUB}}\n|75.49 m\n|29 May 2011\n|<ref>{{cite news|title=World champions Hardee and Ennis set world season leads in G\u00f6tzis - IAAF Combined Events Challenge|url=http://www.iaaf.org/WCE11/news/newsid=60144.html|publisher=[[IAAF]]|author=Diego Sampaolo|date=2011-05-29|accessdate=2011-05-30}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[1500 metres|1500 m]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Ga\u00ebl Qu\u00e9rin]]|FRA}}\n|4:08.90\n|28 May 2017\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=1500m Results|url=https://www.iaaf.org/competitions/iaaf-combined-events-challenge/43rd-hypo-meeting-6077/results/men/decathlon/1500-metres/result#resultheader|publisher=IAAF|date=28 May 2017|accessdate=29 May 2017}}</ref>\n|- bgcolor=\"#e0e0e0\"\n|Women's [[Heptathlon]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Nafissatou Thiam]]|BEL}}\n|7013 points\n|28 May 2017\n|<ref>{{cite news|title=Thiam scores 7013 to break meeting record in G\u00f6tzis|url=https://www.iaaf.org/news/report/hypo-meeting-gotzis-2017-warner-thiam|publisher=IAAF|author=Diego Sampaolo|date=28 May 2017|accessdate=28 May 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[100 metres hurdles|100 m hurdles]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Nadine Visser]]|NED}}\n|12.78 <small>(+1.0 m/s))</small>\n|27 May 2017\n|<ref>{{cite news|title=Thiam and Johnson-Thompson closely matched while Warner comfortably leads in G\u00f6tzis|url=https://www.iaaf.org/